# Data Engineering Learning

A personal learning project focused on building a modern data engineering pipeline using the Medallion Architecture.

## Overview

This project demonstrates how raw data can be extracted from multiple sources, loaded into SQL Server, and transformed through the Bronze, Silver, and Gold layers.

The goal is to learn industry-standard data engineering concepts and best practices by building the entire pipeline from scratch.

## Technologies

- Python
- SQLAlchemy
- Pandas
- Microsoft SQL Server
- SQL Server Management Studio (SSMS)

## Current Progress

- ✅ Database connection
- ✅ Bronze schema creation
- ✅ Bronze table creation
- ✅ Data extraction from CSV files
- ✅ Data loading into SQL Server

